{"tid":2028270,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"晚餐 燒羊架","createTime":"2020-05-21T17:19:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T12:45:52.000Z","uid":62277,"like":13,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"96a7bb6735a6f8a0420b98cdd47aefb522a43615","tid":2028270,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T17:19:28.000Z","msg":"到今日先得閒食老母節飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n揾咗間無咁正式既西餐廳<br />\n價錢唔太貴環境又輕鬆啲<br />\n我揀嗰份係燒羊架配薄荷醬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qxAhV2q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqxAhV2q.jpg&h=57cf4ab5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n簡單咁用鹽吊下味已經夠香口<br />\n肉質腍嫩有羶香<br />\n係稍嫌在個醬做得唔夠清新<br />\n<br />\n覺得呢間餐廳整體都比一般港式西餐做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f43def30d22750636b0e8ec878243cb2f7e34fd0","tid":2028270,"uid":259400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T17:22:08.000Z","msg":"抵唔抵食"},{"pid":"1d1609fed1c1090182f942c5e084833db81fe2c7","tid":2028270,"uid":313974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T17:29:02.000Z","msg":"邊間"},{"pid":"245a635d12f45b7f51ded3c4abf967f3063312f5","tid":2028270,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f43def30d22750636b0e8ec878243cb2f7e34fd0","tid":2028270,"uid":259400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T17:22:08.000Z","msg":"抵唔抵食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T17:48:39.000Z","msg":"又唔算好抵<br />\n但食物質素對得住價錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7709f38f2427faa66238cfd802db41347bfd8b64","tid":2028270,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1d1609fed1c1090182f942c5e084833db81fe2c7","tid":2028270,"uid":313974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T17:29:02.000Z","msg":"邊間"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T17:49:34.000Z","msg":"original art<img src=\"/assets/faces/n